OL,5, The father of a cyclist killed by a    
OL,6, driver who failed to brake or swerve   
OL,7, before the fatal crash said the        
OL,8, decision to spare him jail was a farce.
OL,10,FTony Jones said his family's lives were
OL,11,Ftorn apart when his son David, 41, was 
OL,12,Fkilled in Bridgend in May 2020.        
OL,14,FRaymond Treharne, 74, was given a      
OL,15,Fnine-month suspended sentence and a    
OL,16,Fseven-year driving ban for causing his 
OL,17,Fdeath by careless driving last month.  
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Justice said           
OL,20,Findependent judges decided sentences.  
